sequenceDiagram
    %% Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
        participant Client as Client<br/>(UI / CLI / SDK)
        participant AuthProxy as Platform Auth Proxy<br/>(Istio / kube-rbac-proxy)
        participant MR as Model Registry<br/>REST API Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant DB as MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>or PostgreSQL 5432/TCP

        Client->>AuthProxy: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Platform Auth
        AuthProxy->>MR: Forward (authenticated)<br/>HTTP/8080
        MR->>DB: INSERT model metadata<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+<br/>username/password
        DB-->>MR: Result
        MR-->>AuthProxy: 201 Created (JSON)
        AuthProxy-->>Client: Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over K8sAPI,MR: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation (Controller)
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Controller as MR Controller<br/>(controller-runtime)

        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event: InferenceService CR<br/>TLS / ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>MR: GET/POST /api/.../inference_services<br/>HTTP/8080 (InsecureSkipVerify)
        MR-->>Controller: Model metadata
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService finalizers<br/>TLS / ServiceAccount token
    end

    %% Flow 3: CSI Model Download
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 3: CSI Model Download
        participant KServe as KServe Runtime
        participant CSI as mr-storage-initializer<br/>(init container)
        participant Storage as S3 / GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        KServe->>CSI: Invoke init container<br/>model-registry:// URI
        CSI->>MR: GET /api/.../model_artifacts<br/>HTTP/8080
        MR-->>CSI: Artifact with storage URI
        CSI->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Storage credentials
        Storage-->>CSI: Model files
        CSI-->>KServe: Model ready at local path
    end

    %% Flow 4: Async Model Upload
    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over Job,Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job
        participant Job as async-upload Job<br/>(Python)
        participant SrcStorage as Source Storage<br/>(S3/OCI/HuggingFace)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant DstStorage as Destination Storage<br/>(OCI Registry)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>(Fulcio/Rekor/TUF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Job->>SrcStorage: Download model<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Docker auth / HF token
        SrcStorage-->>Job: Model artifacts
        Job->>Sigstore: Sign model/image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>OIDC identity token
        Sigstore-->>Job: Signature
        Job->>DstStorage: Upload to OCI registry<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Docker auth
        DstStorage-->>Job: Push complete
        Job->>MR: Register/update artifact<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer token
        MR-->>Job: Confirmation
    end
